{
  "stem": "25639.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let at least the-- the sick live a little longer, and we didn't touch the sick, not in our cattle car.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know what they did in the others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we got off, and it was this tall grass and the line was so long.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know what was happening, but we had to go in a certain direction and it moved very, very slowly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by this time it was April 1945, and we had no idea how the war is coming along.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just know that the German cities where I was, was being pounded to pulp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, of course, as prisoners, we-- we really wanted to die rather from a bomb than starve to death or beaten to death, and that's-- that's the only time in life that I ever had to-- well, made a decision that, if I'm gonna die, it's going to be from an air raid attack.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, maybe I'll be in a train and-- or maybe I'll be out in the field, and they'll shoot us, but it's not gonna be from starvation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's a form of fighting [? weapon ?] but of course, it probably would have been starvation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was no-- but we were trying to deny it, I think, in some way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we were walking through the tall, mushy grass.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was wet and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] finally, at the very end, when I reached a certain point, I saw some people-- a woman in front of me raised her skirt.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- and they put something into her skirt from burlap sacks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were two burlap sacks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Finally, I saw that one was filled with raw macaroni and-- raw macaroni.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the other one was filled with sugar.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
